      "content": "hey, i was reading some stuff online about the healthcare debate. i can't really get a straight answer anywhere. some people say universal healthcare is a basic human right that everyone should get automatically, but then others say it's just an inefficient government takeover that's gonna ruin the economy. what do u think? which one is actually right?",
